# llm-wiki middleware delegator

## Stack

- Python 3.12, FastAPI, uvicorn, aiosqlite, httpx, pydantic-settings
- Ollama at http://localhost:11434, model: qwen3.6
- SQLite FTS5 for search (wiki.db), markdown files for wiki pages
- uv for package management, ruff for lint/format

## Default indexing & docs

- @FastAPI
- @Pydantic
- @SQLite

## Conventions

- All Ollama calls are async (httpx.AsyncClient)
- Ingest pipeline runs in background asyncio queue, never blocks HTTP response
- Wiki pages: YAML frontmatter + markdown, path: wiki/<type>/<slug>.md
- Raw Q/A JSON: immutable, written once to raw/qa/YYYY-MM-DD/<slug>.json
- SQLite triggers keep FTS5 index in sync — do not manually insert into *_fts tables
- Return 202 Accepted from POST /ingest immediately, pipeline runs async

## Do not

- Use sync sqlite3 — always aiosqlite
- Block the ingest route waiting for Ollama
- Modify raw/ files after creation
- Use ChromaDB — not in scope for this phase